Class FilteringLongIterator

java.lang.Object
com.github.tommyettinger.ds.support.util.FilteringLongIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
LongIterator, Iterator<Long>
public class FilteringLongIterator extends Object implements LongIterator
Wraps a LongIterator so that it skips any items for which filter returns false. You can use a lambda or other predicate that accepts long and returns true or false for the filter here. This has undefined behavior if any items the LongIterator could return are modified during iteration.
You can change both the LongIterator and filter at once using set(LongIterator, LongPredicate) , and can also just change the Iterator with set(LongIterator).
Based very closely on Predicate.PredicateIterator from libGDX, but changed to handle primitive items.
